snippet.title: Pullfrog Playdate Deluxe - Trailer
snippet.description:
Tetris meets frog! A little puzzle platformer made for Pico-8, equal parts fun and challenging. Help a little frog clear as many lines as possible by using its tongue to pull around blocks in the air.
